    (CyberKit::HighPerformanceGPUManager::removeProcessRequiringHighPerformance):
    (CyberKit::HighPerformanceGPUManager::updateState):
    (CyberKit::isiOSAppOnMac): Deleted.
    HighPerformanceGPUManager is PLATFORM(MAC)-only, which is not true
    for MACCATALYST, so delete this dead code.
    
